    "questionText": "<p>Match List - I with List - II.</p>\n<p><style type=\"text/css\">\n.tg  {border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n.tg td{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg th{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  font-weight:normal;overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg .tg-c3ow{border-color:inherit;text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-7btt{border-color:inherit;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-fymr{border-color:inherit;font-weight:bold;text-align:left;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-0pky{border-color:inherit;text-align:left;vertical-align:top}\n</style>\n<table class=\"tg\" style=\"table-layout: fixed; width: 805px;overflow-x:auto;\">\n<colgroup>\n<col style=\"width: 48px\">\n<col style=\"width: 588px\">\n<col style=\"width: 34px\">\n<col style=\"width: 135px\">\n</colgroup>\n<thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th class=\"tg-7btt\"></th>\n    <th class=\"tg-fymr\">List - I<br>Reaction</th>\n    <th class=\"tg-7btt\"></th>\n    <th class=\"tg-fymr\">List - II<br>Catalyst</th>\n  </tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">(A)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">$$4N{H_3}(g) + 5{O_2}(g) \\to 4NO(g) + 6{H_2}O(g)$$</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">(I)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">$$NO(g)$$</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">(B)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">$${N_2}(g) + 3{H_2}(g) \\to 2N{H_3}(g)$$</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">(II)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">$${H_2}S{O_4}(l)$$</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">(C)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">$${C_{12}}{H_{22}}{O_{11}}(aq) + {H_2}O(l) \\to \\mathop {{C_6}{H_{12}}{O_6}}\\limits_{Glu\\cos e}  + \\mathop {{C_6}{H_{12}}{O_6}}\\limits_{Fructose} $$</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">(III)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">$$Pt(s)$$</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">(D)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">$$2S{O_2}(g) + {O_2}(g) \\to 2S{O_3}(g)$$</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">(IV)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">$$Fe(s)$$</td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></p>\n<p>Choose the correct answer from the options given below :</p>",
